name: THE SINGH FAMILY RESTAURANT & BAR PALOLEM GOA

reviews.review_text: Food was real good but the service took a long time which was about an hour to get the food. Must try their singh special chicken.
We ate the best Pomfret fish in Goa. Ankit served the fish very beautifully. We loved all the details on the plate. The best lunch we had.

Very good food and respectful service. Need more variety of pastas but what they have, they cook and serve well. If the place is full, they will suggest other places and if you are okay with waiting, they take your number and call you for sure. Lovely, humble place and people.
There is this adorable kitten that stole our hearts too!

description:
### Discover the Singh Family Restaurant & Bar in Palolem, Goa

Nestled upon the picturesque shores of Palolem, Goa, the Singh Family Restaurant & Bar stands tall with an impressive rating of 4.6 out of 5, awarded by over 5,700 enthusiastic patrons. This beloved dining spot is celebrated for its beachside charm, tandoori fish specialties, an array of Goan dishes, and notably, its delectable red snapper creations. The restaurant’s commitment to quality and flavor resonates in each review, making it a must-visit for locals and tourists alike seeking an exceptional culinary experience.

### Ambiance & Design

The ambiance of the Singh Family Restaurant is as inviting as the flavors it offers. With a blend of traditional Goan architecture and contemporary decor, the restaurant exudes warmth and character. Soft lighting and vibrant artwork create a relaxed atmosphere for patrons. The inviting feel is complemented by the sound of gentle waves crashing, ensuring that diners can fully savor their meal in a tropical paradise. Reviewers have noted the charming features of the restaurant, including outdoor seating that allows guests to soak in the coastal vibes while enjoying their meals.

![Outdoor Dining Area](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkLULBeihTpiVhUmDHymuBmdSy2Tv4Tomw-J00oSkLIaK43B04XxGdnV3FYEWUBTNrFTqwmDwdbqU6KEgMEi2j5zG3X-VNu3I3uN0gg4nkA9Fg7BS2NwjyPnFDdUzJ2M8fwn2-rgw=w375-h563-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

At the heart of the Singh Family Restaurant lies a menu showcasing the rich flavors of Goan cuisine. Diners rave about the tandoori fish and the much-admired Pomfret fish, particularly the artistic presentation which caught the eye of one patron. The "Singh Special Chicken" has emerged as a signature dish that many revisit for, alongside a more limited pasta selection which some noted could benefit from more variety. For those with specific dietary preferences, the menu offers thoughtful choices, although a bit more pasta variety would be a welcomed addition according to feedback.

![Pomfret Fish Platter](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlAUSK7ASNt-YuQwUIucwK4Rd27trckLTALLS9cPFDoQ6mbaTOT_9W9baiD64qn6xyvW5xNS3opnMy2US4nj4Wv9fMHAhKi0g9hgAmlcf4aDYOFROpJCwUqFmKIi6yGb5ZZQwXd=w375-h563-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

Reviews highlight the friendly demeanor and respectful service provided by the staff at the Singh Family Restaurant. One reviewer mentioned the accommodating nature of the team, suggesting alternative dining options when the restaurant is busy. They also take down guest contact numbers, promising to call once a table is available—a gesture that truly reflects their hospitality ethos. While patrons acknowledged that food service timings can be lengthy at times, the flavors served are well worth the wait. A delightful surprise mentioned in reviews was an adorable kitten that made its rounds, adding to the warm environment.

![Chef's Special Dish](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdni7j6zl8Jd9LZkZRoeAWKTNE_qDJxd1LCWjFZXu9A-fMFUOKolPw5YEvL5YheL2XBaxYvDblMldJM7Zw8lkUGCzIDQ6pfGdAaCVmqjT32XBTmnLwKHumjAd_qu4pGVptu2IHpY7w=w375-h281-p)

### Popularity & Reviews

With a steady stream of favorable reviews, the Singh Family Restaurant has solidified its status as a culinary gem in Goa. The buzz surrounding the venue is palpable on social media, with visitors frequently sharing their marvelous dining experiences. The inviting beachside location, paired with locally sourced ingredients, has earned this establishment a loyal following. Guests appreciate the culinary offerings and cherish the heartfelt service, making it a highlight of their Goan getaway.

In conclusion, whether you’re a seafood aficionado or exploring the rich tapestry of Goan cuisine for the first time, the Singh Family Restaurant & Bar promises an unforgettable dining experience. So, grab your friends and family, and head over to enjoy a delicious meal with a stunning view!
